34
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:48,000
Her emê hetanî jor herin, baş e emê...
 
We will just go up to the top, okay we will...

35
00:03:48,000 --> 00:04:08,000
[Stranbêj]
 
[Singer singing]

36
