55
00:07:50,000 --> 00:08:00,000
[Stranbêj]
 
[Singer singing]

56
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:05,000
Maşala bi şikl am gundê me kurmancan, giran dikan.
 
Mashallah, in general form, our Kurdish villages are
