68
00:08:50,000 --> 00:09:00,000
Mezin e.
 
It is big.

69
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:08,000
Maşala çi tebîetê wehsî çûko kirî. Sibê.
 
Mashallah, what a nature, the birds have made it lively. In
